---
title: Breakfast Bacon and Cheese Flatbreads with Corn and Poblano Pepper
description: Corn, scallions, pepper, cheese, and bacon are the food world equivalent of a boy band. Corn is the sweet and wholesome one. Scallions are more of the brainy, sophisticated type. Pepper is the feisty, fiery life of the party. Cheese is the one who oozes with suave, romantic personality. And bacon? Well, everyone loves bacon—he’s so charismatic and dreamy! Put them together on a flatbread and you’ve got a guaranteed platinum hit recipe.
